<article id="post-883" class="post-883 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-careers category-general tag-critical-mass">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/01/timetracker-is-dead/" rel="bookmark">Timetracker is dead!</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Critical Mass is a service company. We don&#8217;t produce anything physical that we can sell &#8212; it&#8217;s all time. We build websites, yes, but it&#8217;s the <em>time </em>it takes us to make them that counts.<br />
Shortly before I started at Critical Mass, along came TimeTracker. This was the tool used to keep track of the time we were spending. And not in in almost eight years was there a single person who liked it.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/01/timetracker-is-dead/#more-883" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Timetracker is dead!&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/01/timetracker-is-dead/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2008-01-02T08:12:02-07:00">2 January 2008</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/careers/" rel="category tag">Careers</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/critical-mass/" rel="tag">critical mass</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/01/timetracker-is-dead/#comments">2 Comments<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Timetracker is dead!</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
