<article id="post-856" class="post-856 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-careers category-general tag-critical-mass tag-experience-matters">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/11/things-found-in-meeting-rooms-part-1/" rel="bookmark">Things found in meeting rooms, Part 1</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>We keep a clean shop here, making sure that client-sensitive information remains secret and safe. But not every meeting is solely about client work, and sometimes you find something interesting sitting in a meeting room.<br />
In this particular case, I happened to glance up at an easel sitting in the corner of the Ancho Room (the second floor in Calgary has meeting rooms named after peppers), and witnessed a wonderful diagram created by Chrissie, Senior IA in our I&amp;P group.<br />
<a href="http://experiencematters.criticalmass.com/2007/11/02/things-found-in-meeting-rooms-part-1/">Read the rest at Experience Matters!</a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/11/things-found-in-meeting-rooms-part-1/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2007-11-02T08:50:13-06:00">2 November 2007</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/careers/" rel="category tag">Careers</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/critical-mass/" rel="tag">critical mass</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/experience-matters/" rel="tag">experience matters</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/11/things-found-in-meeting-rooms-part-1/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Things found in meeting rooms, Part 1</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
